      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NEEDLE AND SEAT (6) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in her sharp 16.86 win at this track over 300m. Looks the one to beat on win two back. LAST RUPEE (7) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (23.71) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Better than last start and can bounce back. KOORINGA TRISH (4) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.60) at this track behind Western Lies in a Free For All. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Leading chance. REALITY ZERO (1) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
